# Keep the Docker build context lean: the image runs `pnpm install` itself
# (services/api/Dockerfile does COPY . . then installs), so dependency trees
# and build artifacts must never ride along in the context.
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite
**/DerivedData
**/DerivedData-device
apps/roastmyride-app/ios
web/dist
preview/dist
live-panel-out
*.mp4
.git
.claude
